.DT
valid_worshipper
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
valid_worshipper

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
valid_worshipper -  This method checks to see if the worshipper is valid.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int valid_worshipper(string worshipper,
string deity)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^worshipper%^RESET%^ - the worshipper to check
%^BOLD%^deity%^RESET%^ - the deity they should be worshipping according to the handler
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 if they are not valid, 1 if they are
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method checks to see if the worshipper is valid.  This basically
checks to see if they exist and they are worshipping the current deity.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
"/handlers/player_handler"->test_deity()

.EP

